Invocation Name: clickbait title
des:
What does this app do? 
---
Clickbait Title will give you a randomly-generated clickbait title with over one million possibilities of varying length. You can also ask me for a clickbait title regarding any specific subject or person.
Request as many as you like, I won't complain.

How to use:
---

* You: Alexa, open Clickbait Title.
* Alexa: Welcome to Clickbait Title. Ask me for a title...
* You: Alexa, ask Clickbait Title for a title"
* Alexa: Can being liberal actually change your life? True stories from Jay-Z
* You: Alexa, ask Clickbait Title for a title with Donald Trump" 
* The truth behind Donald Trump and Taylor Swift - Just... wow.

And so on...
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
